"Ullrich Haupt (actor born 1887)" 0 Ullrich Haupt (8 August 1887 – 5 August 1931) was a German actor who rose to prominence in Hollywood films. He was the father of Ullrich Haupt Jr., who was also an actor. Haupt died in a hunting accident, three days before his 44th birthday.
